vel up，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冷處理fake news/ rumour</span></strong> 、五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n<em>每星期任務：</em><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">低消費</span>，高儲蓄；罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">做孝子救港</span>，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆</span>貼3張文宣，輸出革命思想<br />\n<br />\n<em>每月任務：</em><br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股，MPF都買美股<br />\n2. 搵多一個人參與<br />\n3. 關心社會、陪審員、派傳單、放映會<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾；Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.13 @Template End@"},{"pid":"88351ab061bc169146401b76f8a514636385fe54","tid":1564311,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:37:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4396198f8ccbb62b6b386c7300dad054bd9a4f91","tid":1564311,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:38:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"276627ce38915c1658bdc1d8d2aadf6b9cbf5c52","tid":1564311,"uid":25598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:38:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79f80b777f2dae371451da150aaee5fc14761b20","tid":1564311,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85db6bab089f228fba1f41b6d6ecc7d7051a4de4","tid":1564311,"uid":1882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5816946e966b3973689e28466848a1f8d79d1453","tid":1564311,"uid":160912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73af5c33622b9c0264bf5596144b5b7a9ebae450","tid":1564311,"uid":173058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:41:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe2db375b13496a7cc3e3889d3b19f22c9766e00","tid":1564311,"uid":15305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:41:55.000Z","msg":"推～"},{"pid"